  "texts": [
    "Query HandlingThe integrated system processes and handles queries through a structured approach that ensures efficient retrieval and utilization of information from the Google Query API.",
    "Upon receiving an input, the system evaluates the need for external information.",
    "If required, a query is constructed based on the input context and dispatched to the API.",
    "The system then awaits the API's response, which upon arrival, is parsed and integrated into the ongoing text generation process.",
    "This integration allows the model to produce outputs that are not only contextually relevant but also enriched with up-to-date information, thereby reducing instances of hallucination and enhancing overall textual quality.The handling of queries is designed to minimize latency and ensure that the flow of text generation remains as uninterrupted as possible."
  ],
